  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎯<strong>The primary objective</strong> is to locate the main character's missing sister, who vanished in the volcanic region. To achieve this, you must gather seven coordinates scattered across two anomalous areas: the metro and the old forest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⌛<strong>Your time</strong> within these hazardous zones is limited, as dangerous creatures await!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤝 Explore unique locations alone or <strong>with a friend</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤑 Find and sell <strong>anomalous items</strong> located in anomalous zones to buy gear and useful equipment!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3524700/extras/609a430dc33860202419fea92d5289b5.poster.avif?t=1763570523\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3524700/extras/609a430dc33860202419fea92d5289b5.webm?t=1763570523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3524700/extras/609a430dc33860202419fea92d5289b5.mp4?t=1763570523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎯<strong>The primary objective</strong> is to locate the main character's missing sister, who vanished in the volcanic region. To achieve this, you must gather seven coordinates scattered across two anomalous areas: the metro and the old forest. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⌛<strong>Your time</strong> within these hazardous zones is limited, as dangerous creatures await!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤝 Explore unique locations alone or <strong>with a friend</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🤑 Find and sell <strong>anomalous items</strong> located in anomalous zones to buy gear and useful equipment!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3524700/extras/609a430dc33860202419fea92d5289b5.poster.avif?t=1763570523\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3524700/extras/609a430dc33860202419fea92d5289b5.webm?t=1763570523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3524700/extras/609a430dc33860202419fea92d5289b5.mp4?t=1763570523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2>",
